This is the Truefire.com course &quot;How to play guitar in 21 days&quot;
All videos have been converted to avi format and combined into day-by-day videos.
eg: all Day 1 videos have been merged into a single file &quot;Day 1.avi&quot; etc.
I have also included all of the .PDF files that were included.

Enjoy, and if you have any other TrueFire courses, or know of any other good Acoustic guitar videos, please leave comment with link.

